item.title: CVE-2022-29094|2024-09-16T16:53:37.826Z -- dell -- supportassist%20client%20consumer
item.description: Dell SupportAssist Client Consumer versions (3.10.4 and versions prior) and Dell SupportAssist Client Commercial versions (3.1.1 and versions prior) contain an arbitrary file deletion/overwrite vulnerability. Authenticated non-admin user could exploit the issue and delete or overwrite arbitrary files on the system.
